972
01:40:51,570 --> 01:40:53,400
You're wrong.

973
01:40:54,260 --> 01:41:01,080
I removed my heart in order to protect other hearts.

974
01:42:18,250 --> 01:42:19,590
Jiro.

975
01:42:37,010 --> 01:42:38,010
