982
01:43:39,360 --> 01:43:44,990
It appears that even my body was imperfect.

983
01:43:45,410 --> 01:43:47,460
Every human is.

984
01:43:47,850 --> 01:43:50,550
We're all imperfect.

985
01:43:54,800 --> 01:43:55,680
Jiro.

986
01:43:58,720 --> 01:44:03,260
This would make for a great novel.

987
01:44:29,620 --> 01:44:30,590
Jiro.

988
01:44:33,810 --> 01:44:34,850
Jiro.

989
01:45:01,990 --> 01:45:02,740
Jiro.

990
01:45:05,690 --> 01:45:10,350
